window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Life was a whole lot easier when the dead stayed dead.</p> <p>I thought I was human. Apparently, I was wrong.</p> <p>I didn't even know there were non-humans. Others, they're called. Fairies, vampires, even the bogeyman - they're all real. At least, that's what the werewolf told me when I saved her from the cops.&nbsp;</p> <p>Did I mention that I saved a werewolf? And those weren't just cops trying to kill her. They're a deadly cult with the sole purpose of capturing and torturing Others...especially me. Because it turns out I'm not just any Other. I can talk to the dead - and this cult has questions only I can answer. Answers they want to use to wipe out every non-human on the planet.</p> <p>My name is Gideon Black, and I'm not human. I am the DeathSpeaker.</p> <p>&nbsp;And I am so screwed.</p>"; 
